# =============================================================================
# .dockerignore - Exclude files from Docker build context
# =============================================================================
# Reduces build context size and speeds up builds significantly

# Git
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.gitattributes

# IDE and editor files
**/.vs
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/.rider
**/*.swp
**/*.swo
**/*.user
**/*.suo

# Build outputs
**/bin
**/obj
**/out
**/publish

# Node modules (if any)
**/node_modules

# Documentation
**/*.md
**/docs
**/documentation

# Docker files (don't include in context)
**/Dockerfile*
**/docker-compose*
**/.dockerignore

# Test projects
**/tests
**/*.Tests
**/*.Test
**/TestResults

# Coverage reports
**/coverage
**/coveragereport

# Local development files
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/appsettings.Development.json
**/appsettings.Local.json

# Data files (should be mounted as volumes)
**/data
**/logs

# macOS
**/.DS_Store

# Windows
**/Thumbs.db

# Temporary files
**/tmp
**/temp
**/*.tmp
**/*.temp
**/*.log

# NuGet
**/*.nupkg
**/.nuget

# Secrets (never include!)
**/*.pfx
**/*.p12
**/*.key
**/*.pem
**/secrets
